{"tid":2346691,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"One Piece 海賊王漫畫同時出現台灣及中國國旗 內地網民呼籲抵制","createTime":"2020-12-30T12:14:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T12:24:26.000Z","uid":8171,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5949f40704947203b8427225987a510b98a8bd02","tid":2346691,"uid":8171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T12:14:55.000Z","msg":"本周是 One Piece 海賊王 1000 期連載的大日子，內地突然在微博很多人談論《海賊王》 ，但跟 1000 期連載沒有關係，而是有內地網民發現某一頁單行本內的彩頁，竟然同時出現台灣及中國國旗。該彩頁全圖包括了不同的國旗，而中國旗上方更有台灣旗出現，令很多中國網友極為不滿，呼籲要抵制 One Piece 海賊王。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/onepiece-china-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2Fonepiece-china-1.jpg&h=06d7dc7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6134c60e49d620d304d3da9c6ba33d20bd285822","tid":2346691,"uid":331590,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T12:24:26.000Z","msg":"點解冇甚平、、、、<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}